<br>
No Drop items goes to those that can use them. try to be fair and distribute as evenly as possible. Random them if there are any problems.<br>
<br>
Droppable items are always rolled on by all. Once you win an item, you don't roll again. Every person gets a droppable item before the first winner can roll again. You can &quot;pass&quot; on a roll that you don't want or can't use. So, if a greedy bastard decides to roll on a 300pp drop that he can't use and wins. He is out of luck when the 5kpp thing that he does need drops. This thought will keep people from rolling on things they don't need for the most part. Any items that everyone passes on will be held by the ML until the camp is over and then distributed between those that got nothing through rolling for them.<br>
<br>
Not perfect, but better than nothing.<br>
<br>
